name: Middletown POD
notes: ●●● ENGLISH: This clinic is offering the Moderna COVID-19 vaccine which is for people age 18 and older only. Para direcciones de llegar a la clínica o información de estacionamiento, visite la siguiente página: https://health.ri.gov/vaccinesiteinfo. ●●● PORTUGUÊS: Esta clínica está a oferecer a vacina COVID-19 da Moderna, que é apenas para pessoas com 18 anos ou mais. If you are signing up for a second dose, you must get the same vaccine brand as your first dose.

Please do not register for it if you are looking for a first dose and are unable to travel off the island in four weeks to get your corresponding second dose, as there will be no second dose Moderna on the island four weeks from this date.
